  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A BATTLE, A TRIAL</h2></strong><br><br>Certain people have been chosen to redeem themselves, the accursed combatants that have misused the forbidden power. As a punishment, they are destined to fight for something called \"Darkened Glory\", a trial that can help them lift the curse if they're worthy enough.<br>Darkened Glory will test your skills in a high-paced, real-time adventure game. Play by yourself or join up with more players.<br>Choose your combatant, whether a mage or a simple warrior, you will start with a small purse of gold that is enough to begin your quest for Darkened Glory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1544110/extras/20abf1caa8f91628e9722bb658224c0b.avif?t=1620507726\" width=601 height=154 /></span><br><br>Be aware that this is an early access and we have 5 classes (with 2 sexes each) provided and 1 class upcoming.<br><br>Currently available classes:<br>-Warrior<br>-Berserker<br>-Mage<br>-Rogue<br>-Necromancer<br><br>SPECIAL FEATURE INCLUDED - LEVEL EDITOR<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1544110/extras/01932e8056d1a4868c1d448f9717f8d4.avif?t=1620507726\" width=734 height=413 /></span><br><br><br>We want to express our gratitude to MatyGex for general support!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A BATTLE, A TRIAL</h2></strong><br><br>Certain people have been chosen to redeem themselves, the accursed combatants that have misused the forbidden power. As a punishment, they are destined to fight for something called \"Darkened Glory\", a trial that can help them lift the curse if they're worthy enough.<br>Darkened Glory will test your skills in a high-paced, real-time adventure game. Play by yourself or join up with more players.<br>Choose your combatant, whether a mage or a simple warrior, you will start with a small purse of gold that is enough to begin your quest for Darkened Glory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1544110/extras/20abf1caa8f91628e9722bb658224c0b.avif?t=1620507726\" width=601 height=154 /></span><br><br>Be aware that this is an early access and we have 5 classes (with 2 sexes each) provided and 1 class upcoming.<br><br>Currently available classes:<br>-Warrior<br>-Berserker<br>-Mage<br>-Rogue<br>-Necromancer<br><br>SPECIAL FEATURE INCLUDED - LEVEL EDITOR<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1544110/extras/01932e8056d1a4868c1d448f9717f8d4.avif?t=1620507726\" width=734 height=413 /></span><br><br><br>We want to express our gratitude to MatyGex for general support!",
